OL,3,CRace hate crimes 'spiralling out of
OL,4,Ccontrol'
OL,6,FA family have been verbally abused and
OL,7,Fhad mud thrown at their home in a
OL,8,Fracially motivated attack in Co
OL,9,FLondonderry.
OL,11,FPolice said they had engaged with "a
OL,12,Fnumber of young people" with regards
OL,13,Fto the incident in the Strathfoyle
OL,14,Farea of Derry.
OL,16,FThe attack comes as PSNI statistics
OL,17,Fshow police recorded more than 1,500
OL,18,Fracist hate crimes and nearly 2,500
OL,19,Fracist incidents in the year to March
OL,20,F2026.
OL,26,@sD@cOUtD@WO]
