OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1779034269
OL,3,CRace hate crimes 'spiralling out of
OL,4,Ccontrol'
OL,6,F"Tackling racism and race hate crime
OL,7,Fin Northern Ireland requires not just
OL,8,Fa consistent response from the police
OL,9,Fbut clear leadership from the
OL,10,FExecutive."
OL,12,FPolice recorded 1,507 racist hate
OL,13,Fcrimes and 2,367 racist incidents in
OL,14,Fthe 12 months to the end of March
OL,15,F2026, an increase of 561 incidents
OL,16,Fcompared with the previous 12 months.
